# Chat Room â€“ Real-time Room Code Chat App

A simple and lightweight real-time chat application built with **Node.js**, **Express**, and **Socket.IO**.  
Users can create or join rooms using a **room code** and a **maximum member limit**, making it ideal for quick private group chats.

ğŸ”— **Repository:** https://github.com/SaiKumar2121/chat-room

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Create a chat room with a custom room code
- Choose how many members are allowed (e.g., 2, 4, custom)
- Share room code with others to join
- Real-time chat using Socket.IO
- Prevent additional users from joining if room is full

---

## ğŸ§° Tech Stack

- **Node.js**
- **Express.js**
- **Socket.IO**
- **HTML / CSS / Vanilla JavaScript**

