## ğŸ§  How It Works (Simple Explanation)

* When a user creates a room:

  * Server stores the room with `maxMembers`
  * Room is created only once (first user)
* When someone joins:

  * Server checks if the room exists
  * Checks if capacity is full
  * If not full â†’ user joins successfully
  * Server broadcasts messages using:

    ```js
    io.to(roomCode).emit("chat-message", payload);
    ```

