## ğŸ”§ Development Tips

### Optional: Use nodemon for auto-reload

```bash
npm install --save-dev nodemon
```

Add to `package.json`:

```json
"scripts": {
  "start": "node server.js",
  "dev": "nodemon server.js"
}
```

Start with:

```bash
npm run dev
```

